---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} schema={schema}>
  <ModernHero
    tone="light"
    title="Together, We Solve."
    intro="In an industry that never stops evolving, Found Search Marketing stands out as an agency that knows exactly who we are. Grounded in a deep commitment to our clients, we combine precision with agility to thrive in a fast-moving world. We're proud cool nerds, energized by the pursuit of high-ceiling, complex problems that drive significant business impact."
    cta={{ label: 'Join Our Team', href: '/about-us/' }}
    image={{
      src: 'https://foundsm.com/found2025/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/tr-andy-ryan.webp',
      alt: 'Found Search Marketing team members collaborating',
      width: 1000,
      height: 700,
      loading: 'eager',
    }}
  />

  <StatementBand
    lead="While many chase the next shiny idea, we stay focused, unapologetically ourselves."
    body="Our clients have access to the people behind their brand. Unlike traditional agencies, Found is built to foster cross-functional expertise. Our integrated team structure breaks down silos and acts as a catalyst for client-focused strategy, deep analysis, and results-driven execution."
  />

  <LeadershipGrid
    title="Leadership"
    intro={[
      "At Found, leadership isn't just about setting direction: it's about driving innovation, empowering each other to ask hard questions, and navigating complexity with care and intent to transform challenges into breakthroughs. Our executive team brings decades of hands-on experience in paid media, data engineering and analytics, and customer acquisition strategy, including foundational roles at Google.",
      "Found's leadership stays close to the work, thinks like clients, and focuses on results. That's helped build an agency culture rooted in innovation, precision, and high-impact collaboration.",
    ]}
    leaders={leaders}
  />

  <CtaPanel
    theme="green"
    title="Want to Join Our Team?"
    body="We're always looking for people who share our passion for finding smart, innovative solutions for our clients and are excited to grow with a company. Sound like you? Let's chat."
    ctaLabel="Discover Your New Career"
    ctaHref="/about-us/#careers"
  />
</BaseLayout>
